author: kahatlen
msg: DERBY-6371: DROP COLUMN looks in wrong schema when checking trigger dependencies
Fix another occurrence where the wrong schema is used. This occurrence
doesn't cause any problems currently, since it's only used for
parsing, and the problems wouldn't appear until one attempt to do
binding with the incorrect schema. Fix it anyway for consistency.

author: rombert
msg: SLING-3097 - Track bundle deployment operations in the Sling console
Add a TracingOsgiClient which optionally wraps the main OsgiClient, if
The Maven deployment was not instrumented to display in the Sling
console since it opens its own console when running.
